hist(vastchs$AGE,main="Age distribution of study participants", 
     xlab="Age (years)", ylab="nb", col="green", border="dark green",
     breaks=5)
```

With Tidyverse

```{r}
ggplot(vastchs, aes(x=AGE)) +
